Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.45,mianze2,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fsp10\c&H7738B1&\pos(913.004,238.572)}笔名 梦野咲子
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.87,mianze2,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fsp10\c&H7738B1&\pos(230.719,102.572)}故事
